room_title: Escape room "Sherlock's Study" by Escape May in Cape May
room_description: After discovering that Lord Blackwood is a fraud whose supernatural feats are nothing but the work of science and trickery, Sherlock Holmes has been arrested!  You and your team of detectives must unravel the clues twisted up in a web of lies and illusions to stop the genius mastermind from using a chemical weapon that poses a threat to all of London.
